(451, '34.35', 263, 'Customer Support Specialist with Danish/French/Czech/German/Hebrew', '', '', '         <!--opis_firmy-->Manpower is dedicated to enriching people&apos;s lives with meaningful employment and development opportunities, as we have done for more than 60 years. With our global presence and local expertise, and by leveraging the expertise of our parent company, ManpowerGroup, we influence how people and companies work now and how they will work in the future.<br/>Customer Support Specialist with Danish/French/Czech/German/Hebrew<br/><br/><!--end--><!--obowiazki-->Responsibilities: <ul><li>Effectively manage incoming telephone and e-mail customer&apos;s queries to ensure excellent service standards</li> <li>Provide product/ services information and resolve any emerging problems that our clients might face with accuracy and efficiency</li> <li>Assist with placement of orders, refunds or exchanges</li> <li>Identify and assess customer&apos;s needs to achieve satisfaction</li> <li>Communicate in positive manner with team members and business partners</li> </ul><!--end--><!--kwalifikacje-->What we expect? <ul><li>Fluent knowledge of <strong>one of the languages: French/Czech/Danish/German/Hebrew</strong></li> <li>Communicative knowledge of English min. B1</li> <li>Availability to shift work</li> <li>Experience in a similar position will be an advantage</li> <li>Willingness to acquire new knowledge</li> </ul><!--end--><!--oferta-->We offer: <ul><li>Attractive salary</li> <li>Opportunity to gain practical work experience in large, modern and recognizable company</li> <li>Multinational environment with high standard of work</li> <li>A wide range of social benefits</li> </ul><div><br />Read the job offer in polish: https://bit.ly/2RuMpnU</div><!--end-->       ', '', '', '', '0.00', 'PLN', 0, 0, 'Polska', 'łódzkie', 'Łódź', '', '', '', 1554073506, 1556665506, 30, '', '', '', '1554073506', 1, 1, 1, 0, '', 'pl', '', '2019/04/01', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, '10287441